      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for a fixer-upper or a budget project car? This vehicle runs and drives but is in poor condition \u2014 it has notable mechanical issues and cosmetic wear that will need attention. It's a great opportunity for a handy buyer, a DIY mechanic, or someone looking for a parts car or affordable learner vehicle. Priced honestly to reflect its current state \u2014 what you see is what you get, no surprises!",
