    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is presented in absolutely mint condition \u2014 an exceptional find in today's used car market. The exterior is pristine, showcasing original factory paint with a deep, rich gloss that is entirely free of scratches, dents, chips, or fading. Every panel aligns perfectly, and the trim and chrome accents remain bright and unblemished. The interior is equally immaculate: seats, carpets, dashboard, and headliner all appear as though the car just rolled off the showroom floor, with no stains, tears, or wear marks of any kind. All electronic systems, controls, and displays function flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean and well-maintained, with no leaks, corrosion, or signs of neglect. The tires retain strong tread depth and wear evenly, and all mechanical systems \u2014 brakes, suspension, steering, and transmission \u2014 operate smoothly and responsively. Service records are up to date and available for review. This is a rare opportunity to own a used vehicle that genuinely rivals a new car in both appearance and performance. Priced to reflect its outstanding condition.",
      "price": 48000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
