      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is priced to reflect that honestly. The exterior shows significant wear including deep scratches, paint fading, rust spots, and multiple dents or dings across the body panels. The interior is heavily worn with torn or stained upholstery, damaged trim pieces, and signs of prolonged heavy use. Mechanically, the car has known issues that will likely require attention \u2014 it may start and move, but buyers should expect to invest in repairs. This listing is best suited for buyers comfortable with a project vehicle, those seeking parts, or mechanically inclined individuals who want to restore or repair it themselves. A pre-purchase inspection by a trusted mechanic is strongly recommended before committing to this purchase.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
