    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly exceptional vehicle that has been meticulously maintained from day one. Every surface, system, and component reflects the care of an owner who treated this car as an investment. The exterior gleams with a flawless finish, the interior remains spotless and factory-fresh, and every mechanical element performs exactly as intended. Pre-sale inspection records are available, and the vehicle history is clean and fully documented. If you've been searching for a used car that feels anything but used, your search ends here.",
      "price": 44900.0,
