    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 I'm thrilled to share this absolute gem with you today. This beauty is in truly mint condition \u2014 we're talking a car that turns heads every single time it rolls down the street. The paint is deep and lustrous with that showroom shine, the interior is spotless and smells fresh, and everything under the hood purrs like it just rolled off the assembly line. I've taken meticulous care of this one, keeping up with every service interval and storing it properly. Honestly, finding a car in this kind of shape is rare, and I'd love to see it go to someone who'll appreciate it as much as I have. Come take a look \u2014 I promise you won't be disappointed. Let's talk!",
      "price": 46000.0,
