      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "2021 BMW M340i xDrive \u2014 Zero-compromise daily driver presenting in true turn-key condition. The S58-adjacent B58 inline-six breathes freely through its twin-scroll turbocharger, delivering instantaneous throttle response across the entire powerband. Transmission shifts are crisp and decisive via the 8-speed ZF automatic, with paddle-shift response times that rival dedicated sport units. All four corners ride on factory-spec adaptive dampers with no perceptible fade or compliance degradation \u2014 geometry is tight, bushings are fresh, and the steering rack communicates road texture with surgical precision. Full service history documented, OEM brake components showing minimal wear, and all fluid intervals addressed ahead of schedule. Interior surfaces are free of wear patterns, bolster compression, or UV degradation. Exterior finish retains factory depth with no clear-coat fatigue, swirl marks, or panel inconsistencies. This is the rare example that drives exactly as it presents \u2014 a genuine driver's machine at the top of its game.",
      "price": 47500.0,
